text: René Theo van Dieren (born 12 March 1981 in Naarden) is a Dutch retired footballer. ==Club career== His former clubs are Fortuna Sittard, Feyenoord, Excelsior,Excelsior gaat afscheid nemen van Van Dieren - Voetbal International AGOVV ApeldoornRené van Dieren op proef bij AGOVV - and Sparta Rotterdam.René van Dieren bereikt overeenstemming met Sparta Rotterdam - Sparta He finished his career at FC Lienden in the Dutch Topklasse.Van Dieren naar FC Lienden - Rijnmond ==International career== He was a member of the Dutch squad at the 2001 FIFA World Youth Championship and the 2013 FIFA Beach Soccer World Cup. ==References== ==External links== * Voetbal International profile * VoetbalFocus Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:People from Naarden Category:Association football midfielders Category:Dutch footballers Category:Netherlands youth international footballers Category:Dutch beach soccer players Category:Feyenoord players Category:Fortuna Sittard players Category:SBV Excelsior players Category:AGOVV Apeldoorn players Category:Sparta Rotterdam players Category:FC Lienden players Category:Eredivisie players Category:Eerste Divisie players Category:Derde Divisie players
